STATE EX REL. WARE
v.
MONTGOMERY CTY. CLERK OF COURTS 2018-1012 Supreme Court of Ohio. October 10, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, Fischer, and DeWine, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus. On motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed.

French and DeGenaro, JJ., dissent and would grant an alternative writ.
